These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, orchid
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros, vegafina
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsorchid##2
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of trance is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Flower   | rose     | daffodil | orchid |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Cigar     | oliveros     | montecristo      | vegafina |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, badminton
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, october
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Sport   | badminton  | skiing | biathlon |
| Birthday           | october | january     | august       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, russian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, july
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the american is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the argentine##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality          | american  | russian     | argentine     |
| Birthday           | july | january  | march   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, poker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, techno, house
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the paramedic and the person playing domino##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Game     | snooker   | poker | domino        |
| Music-Genre   | house | disco     | techno      |

