.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, fanta
There are 3 different nationalities: french, pakistani, american
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the french is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the french is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Beverage   | fanta  | hot-chocolate       | milk       |
| Nationality           | pakistani     | french       | american     |

