.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, drama, horror
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, green
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | drama | crime | horror    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Color   | orange   | chestnut     | green        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

