.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, almond-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, chaman, swisher
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person eating radish and the person driving the car##2
3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking almond-milk and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Beverage         | mirinda | cola | almond-milk |
| Cigar   | siglo      | swisher | chaman   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

