2. the russian is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person eating lemon is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the pakistani##2
5. the russian is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Nationality      | spanish       | russian      | pakistani      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | rock-climbing | chess      |
| Food           | artichoke | lemon     | kale |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

