The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, february, june
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing canasta##2
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Birthday          | february   | november      | june     |
| Game   | canasta  | monopoly      | backgammon |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

