.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, drawing, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, social-worker
City: miami, new-york, marseilles
3 different games are played: chess, poker, bridge
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the project-manager is between the engineer and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is the social-worker##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person playing chess is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager | engineer |
| City       | new-york      | marseilles         | miami |
| Game   | chess        | bridge            | poker  |

