1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
4. the person eating pepper is between the person playing bridge and the person playing canasta##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
