3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person driving the car and the person who's birthday is in april##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
