.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
City: rome, london, boston
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, backgammon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person traveling to boston is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| City      | london    | boston          | rome |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Game           | snooker | backgammon | domino         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

