3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who likes grey##2
5. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Color          | aquamarine  | fuchsia   | grey |
