.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, backgammon
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, baseball
1. the german is between the person who's sport is baseball and the egyptian##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Game   | monopoly | mah-jongg  | backgammon     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Sport     | baseball      | surfing   | rowing |

