2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Sport           | weightlifting   | snowboarding   | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| City           | paris | liverpool | rome    |

