.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy, aconite
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, green
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes green##1
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | marigold | aconite     | daisy        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Color   | ivory        | fuchsia       | green      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

