.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: canasta, poker, chess
House: cottage, farmhouse, tower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the car##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person playing chess##1
5. the tower house is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Game        | poker      | canasta | chess |
| House         | farmhouse     | tower    | cottage        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 